{"tid":865582,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《湯姆與謝利》推真人版動畫電影 傳《神奇4俠》系列導演執導","createTime":"2018-10-17T07:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T10:44:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bdba7cf884246a3bb7f8f9ca889e4f6b3489f8ff","tid":865582,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1979855/org/66802f6140d6576178f9115d02ae3e73.jpg/wwka7TJQiEgFFHY5kDz1TqOrYDHmvP-Rwb9OJ8G_Tic?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1979855%2Forg%2F66802f6140d6576178f9115d02ae3e73.jpg%2Fwwka7TJQiEgFFHY5kDz1TqOrYDHmvP-Rwb9OJ8G_Tic%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ff2aeb7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華納兄弟自從2014年推出《LEGO英雄傳》（The Lego Movie）動畫電影後，該系列動畫電影一直獲得不俗口碑，其後還推出包括《LEGO英雄傳2》、《LEGO蝙蝠俠英雄傳》、《LEGO旋風忍者大電影》及《電影少年悍將 GO！》等動畫電影。如今華納兄弟積極拓展動畫製作部，據了解，他們正研究拍攝《湯姆與謝利》（Tom and Jerry）真人版電影。《神奇4俠》（Fantastic Four）系列導演Tim Story盛傳將擔任該真人版動畫電影導演。<br />\n<br />\n《湯姆與謝利》由著名動畫大師William Hanna及Joseph Barbera共同創立，並於1940年首次跟大眾會面。該動畫集中描繪兩位主角湯姆與謝利之間永無止境的惡作劇。當時《湯姆與謝利》深受大眾喜愛，時任發行商美高梅（MGM）更曾憑7齣不同的《湯姆與謝利》短片，7奪奧斯卡最佳動畫短片獎。<br />\n<br />\n《湯姆與謝利》一直以來歷久不衰，並在1993年推出首部長篇電影《Tom and Jerry:The Movie》，惟當時香港並沒有上映，在2002年才以影音光碟形式發行。<br />\n<br />\n除了《湯姆與謝利》真人版動畫電影外，盛傳華納還有意重啟另一套動畫電影《狗狗震》（Scooby-Doo），然而今次卻非以真人版動畫電影形式製作。據了解，該動畫電影暫定由《哈利波特：神秘的魔法石》（Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone）導演Chris Columbus擔任創作總監。"},{"pid":"5e7fcc45e47c8d32022ac2170836291b8cbc3efe","tid":865582,"uid":158994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:34:47.000Z","msg":"揾人扮貓定揾真貓拍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56df36b55eec0a022c1db256ed43ce854b4d803a","tid":865582,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"我想睇肥貓大戰三小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27816fe1881342f852a56e9925c1b29298599428","tid":865582,"uid":35217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e7fcc45e47c8d32022ac2170836291b8cbc3efe","tid":865582,"uid":158994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:34:47.000Z","msg":"揾人扮貓定揾真貓拍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:39:39.000Z","msg":"真人版動畫<br />\n即係好似paddington 藍精靈嗰d咁用cg整出黎啦"},{"pid":"afb95615255762fb85270bab90dbac56df4abcc1","tid":865582,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:47:30.000Z","msg":"呢套野真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6330946499ce955098fdb2b3fdf6d2f3be80a94d","tid":865582,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"呢套野暫時一集最長嘅動畫版係幾分鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d32ca64211065944f7c10e6d9ce778f11f04e40","tid":865582,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6091ce0a3442ac9d548439ce11e79b39e9771962","tid":865582,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27816fe1881342f852a56e9925c1b29298599428","tid":865582,"uid":35217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e7fcc45e47c8d32022ac2170836291b8cbc3efe","tid":865582,"uid":158994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:34:47.000Z","msg":"揾人扮貓定揾真貓拍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim